ht|e|cs|6|at|^l{|ia|1dp1s2cX|at|}|ht|d|cs||at|^kQuestion 1 - by Larry Cohen|hf|j|lb|*mWhat is the name of the convention whereby West's Double above shows 3 cards in spades?^Takeout Double~Negative Double~Support Double~Responsive Double^3|
